Thai Premier Faces Grilling Over Philip Morris Case, Nation Says

-- B y   D a n i e l   T e n   K a t e
-- 
2011-03-07T02:14:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/thai-premier-faces-grilling-over-philip-morris-case-nation-says.html
  Thailand ’s main opposition party
Puea Thai plans to grill Prime Minister Abhisit Vejjajiva over
allegations that he helped Philip Morris (Thailand) Ltd evade
taxes, the Nation reported, citing Yuthapong Jarassathian, the
party’s deputy spokesman.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
